OL,7,FHanson, 46, appeared at Derby Crown
OL,8,FCourt on Monday charged with
OL,9,Fcontrolling or coercive behaviour,
OL,10,Fassault occasioning actual bodily
OL,11,Fharm, and assault by beating.
OL,13,FMrs Hanson told the jury that "over
OL,14,Fthe next 10 years" after it began, her
OL,15,Fhusband would be violent towards her
OL,16,F"every six months or so".
