OL,14,FJune 2023 and "denied having grabbed,
OL,15,Fpoked or squeezed" his wife, during a
OL,16,Fpolice interview.
OL,18,FThe charge of controlling or coercive
OL,19,Fbehaviour against Hanson's wife
OL,20,Frelates to a period between 2015 and
OL,21,F2023.
